BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:<a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/?Input=&lineIds=&dateTypeSelect=Future%20date&direction=&startDate=2026-04-21T11:00:00&endDate=2026-04-22T10:59:00">Disruption map.</a>\n\nTUBE STRIKE: Some London Underground Tube drivers are planning to take strike action on the following dates and times: From 1200 Tuesday 21 until 1159 Wednesday 22 April\, from 1200 Thursday 23 until 1159 Friday 24 April\, from 1200 Tuesday 19 until 1159 Wednesday 20 May\, from 1200 Thursday 21 until 1159 Friday 22 May\, from 1200 Tuesday 16 until 1159 Wednesday 17 June and from 1200 Thursday 18 until 1159 Friday 19 June. On the affected Tuesdays and Thursdays\, Tube services will run normally in the morning. Severe disruption is expected once the strike begins. On Wednesdays and Friday\, severe disruption is expected to continue until midday\, when the strike ends\, but disruption is likely through the afternoon and evening.
DTEND:20260422T105900Z
DTSTART:20260421T110000Z
SUMMARY:Waterloo & City: Special Service
UID:98e2405f-fcc7-46b4-871b-6cde35f7a720@98e2.org
